    "CatchLine": "Expands definition of \"outdoor mass gathering\" to include certain rural gatherings.",
    "MinorityCatchLine": null,
    "MeasureSummary": "\tExpands definition of \"outdoor mass gathering\" to include certain rural gatherings. \n\tAllows counties to require outdoor mass gathering <b>of more than 3,000 people</b>, except agri-tourism events, to obtain land use permit. \n\tAllows counties to charge larger fee for approval of larger outdoor mass gathering.",
